title.narrative: Tanzania - Support to Maternal Mortality Reduction Project
Tanzanie - Projet d’appui à la réduction de la mortalité maternelle

description.narrative: The objective of the Support to Maternal Mortality Reduction Project is to accelerate the reduction of maternal and newborn deaths in Mara, Mtwara, Tabora and Zanzibar by strengthening health infrastructure and training health personnel for the provision of maternal and newborn health services. The project comprises three components: (i) Component I - Strengthened Delivery of Maternal Health Services (Mainland), (ii) Component II - Strengthened Delivery of Health Care Services (Zanzibar), and (iii) Component III - Management and Coordination.
